    "## Section 2 - PyTorch Dataset & DataLoader\n",
    "### 3.1 - Custom Dataset Class  *(Pre-processing)*\n",
    "The `BoneFractureDataset` class:\n",
    "1. Reads YOLOv8 polygon labels and converts them to axis-aligned bounding boxes.\n",
    "2. **Pre-processing:** normalises pixel values from `[0, 255]` -> `[0.0, 1.0]` (division by 255).\n",
    "3. Returns images as `(C, H, W)` float tensors and targets as dicts required by TorchVision Faster R-CNN.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-03-17T17:47:48.463469Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-03-17T17:47:48.463212Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-03-17T17:47:55.710515Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-03-17T17:47:55.709866Z",
     "shell.execute_reply.started": "2026-03-17T17:47:48.463438Z"
    },
